---
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <img
    src="/images/drive-new/wisuda/wisuda-2.webp"
    alt="Santri wisuda hafidz Al-Qur'an"
    width="1920"
    height="1080"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
    loading="eager"
  />
  <!-- Dark overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-900/85 via-primary-900/70 to-primary-900/60"></div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center">
    <!-- Gold divider -->
    <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-secondary-500 mx-auto rounded mb-4"></div>

    <!-- Urgency pill -->
    <div class="inline-block bg-coral-500/20 text-coral-300 text-sm px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 font-medium">
      Target Bulanan: Rp 150.000.000 — Terkumpul Rp 85.000.000
    </div>

    <!-- Problem Headline -->
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white font-heading leading-tight mb-4">
      250 Santri Menghafal Al-Qur'an<br class="hidden sm:block" />
      <span class="text-secondary-400">Bergantung Pada Bantuan Kita</span> Setiap Hari
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtitle — the struggle -->
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      Mereka bangun sebelum subuh untuk menghafal ayat-ayat Allah. Tapi setiap hari, 250 santri
      berjuang melawan keterbatasan — pangan yang pas-pasan, listrik yang sering putus di malam hari,
      dan fasilitas belajar yang jauh dari layak.
    </p>

    <!-- Impact line -->
    <p class="text-base text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 italic">
      "Rp 50.000 dari Anda = makan 2 santri selama sehari. Rp 100.000 = penerangan belajar 1 pekan."
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <button
        onclick="event.preventDefault();window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('campaign:donate',{detail:{campaign:'general',campaignLabel:'Donasi Sekarang'}}))"
        class="bg-coral-500 hover:bg-coral-600 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-200 shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium"
        &#10084; Saya Ingin Membantu
      </button>
      <a
        href="#program"
        class="border-2 border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Lihat Program Donasi
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
